OL,3,CFormer Reform leader in Wales Nathan
OL,4,CGill faces jail for Russian bribes
OL,6,FThe former leader of Reform UK in
OL,7,FWales has arrived in court and is
OL,8,Ffacing jail after admitting making pro-
OL,9,FRussian statements in the European
OL,10,FParliament for cash.
OL,12,FNathan Gill, 52, of Anglesey, North
OL,13,FWales, will be sentenced on Friday at
OL,14,Fthe Old Bailey after previously
OL,15,Fpleading guilty to eight counts of
OL,16,Fbribery on dates between December 6
OL,17,F2018 and July 18 2019.
