OL,3,CFormer Reform leader in Wales Nathan
OL,4,CGill faces jail for Russian bribes
OL,6,FHis activities were said to include
OL,7,Fmaking pro-Russian statements about
OL,8,Fevents in Ukraine in the European
OL,9,FParliament and in opinion pieces to
OL,10,Fnews outlets, such as 112 Ukraine.
OL,12,FAt a previous hearing, Mark Heywood
OL,13,FKC, prosecuting, said the offences
OL,14,Frelated to Gill's time as a member of
OL,15,Fthe European Parliament, having been
OL,16,Foriginally elected for the UK
OL,17,FIndependence Party (Ukip).
