OL,3,CFormer Reform leader in Wales Nathan
OL,4,CGill faces jail for Russian bribes
OL,6,FHe remained an elected member of the
OL,7,FEuropean Parliament until the UK left
OL,8,Fthe union in 2020 and was a member of
OL,9,Fthe Welsh National Assembly for part
OL,10,Fof that period, the court was told.
OL,12,FThe bribery offences related to Gill's
OL,13,Fassociation with pro-Russian Oleg
OL,14,FVoloshyn, who had been a Ukrainian
OL,15,Fgovernment official before 2014, Mr
OL,16,FHeywood said.
