OL,6,FMr Voloshyn, who also became member of
OL,7,Fthe Ukrainian parliament, had links to
OL,8,Fmedia outlets such as 112 Ukraine,
OL,9,Fwith which his wife was associated,
OL,10,Fthe court heard.
OL,12,FGill's activities emerged in WhatsApp
OL,13,Fmessages on his phone after he was
OL,14,Fstopped at Manchester Airport on
OL,15,FSeptember 13 2021 under the Counter
OL,16,FTerrorism and Border Security Act 2019.
