OL,6,FThe messages showed communication
OL,7,Fbetween Gill and Mr Voloshyn of an
OL,8,F"agreement to receive money in
OL,9,Fconnection with his performance in his
OL,10,Fduties as a member of the European
OL,11,FParliament", Mr Heywood said.
OL,13,FThey included "posing questions for
OL,14,Fthe consideration of (the European)
OL,15,Fparliament, making contact with senior
OL,16,Fofficials of the European Commission
OL,17,Fat the parliament, arranging for
OL,18,Fevents and making statements", the
OL,19,Fprosecutor told the court.
