OL,6,FAfter the airport stop, counter
OL,7,Fterrorism detectives also seized
OL,8,Fdevices from Gill's home in north
OL,9,FWales, police said.
OL,11,FInvestigators matched WhatsApp
OL,12,Fmessages with statements Gill had made
OL,13,Fin support of pro-Russia media being
OL,14,Fpresent in Ukraine. Some of the
OL,15,Fstatements appeared in Ukrainian media.
