OL,6,FWhen he was interviewed by police in
OL,7,FMarch 2022, Gill made no comment and
OL,8,Fwas charged in January 2025. Gill
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to eight bribery
OL,10,Fcharges but denied one charge of
OL,11,Fconspiracy to commit bribery.
